text: Atangana is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Charles Atangana (circa 1880-1943), Cameroonian traditional ruler * Jean-Marie Atangana Mebara (born 1954), Cameroonian politician * Marie-Thérèse Catherine Atangana Assiga Ahanda, Cameroonian novelist and chemist * Robert Atangana (born 1966), Cameroonian Entrepreneur * Mvondo Atangana (born 1979), Cameroonian footballer
